text: Now that there’s no more money to be made holding cryptocurrencies, our last chance at pre-AGI wealth is farming USDC by posting bangers on the lavender application

We're making some tweaks to the Warpcast rewards algo based on your feedback. 

First a quick recap on how scoring worked last week: 

1. For each cast, get points for likes, recasts, follows 
2. Only count engagement from known good users
3. Divide by sqrt(active followers) where (active = last 7 days)

the keys to successful farcasting:

1. talking about whatever u find interesting
2. replying to whatever u find interesting
3. trying things u find interesting
4. being nice to ppl

that’s it

“What do I find interesting?”

My hunch is a lot of people in general (maybe more so outside of farcaster than here) can’t answer this question. 

If you can answer it, consider yourself a lucky one.  If your list is long, you’re especially lucky.

text:
Wrote something new about a project I'm really excited about.

Between Farcade, Castout, Clankermon, Farville, Bracket and all the other games we’re lucky to have, I know there are some seriously competitive people on the purple app.

And I have something special just for you today.

The team from RekTech has handed me some OG roles and a handful of Free Mint Passes to give away on Farcaster. 

I love RekTech’s games because they don’t take a ton of time, they’re easy to learn, and everyone’s on equal footing. 
 
If you think you have what it takes to compete in RekTech’s mini-games and tourneys and wanna win a pass, check out my new post. 

In fact, I’ll give away the first OG roles now.

Hop in the discord and tell ‘em Sparkz sent you. Screenshot proof in the replies and I’ll pick a couple winners later today. 

https://paragraph.xyz/@futureproof/rektech-a-new-breed-of-crypto-gaming

RekTech is ‘the world’s craziest’ game show, where you fight to the digital death in a variety of fun, easy to play mini-games. A crypto battle royale, if you will. Where the last degens standing get something money can't buy ... bragging rights 😅 Ok ok ... there's some incredible prizes like blue-chip NFTs and tokens too....
